## Edge Cases Handled

| Scenario | Behavior |
|----------|----------|
| "What is the weather?" | Routes to Avi (question detected) |
| "@link-logger check this url" | Routes to link-logger (explicit mention) |
| "https://example.com cool site" | Routes to link-logger (URL detected) |
| "Avi help me" | Routes to Avi (explicit mention) |
| "aviation news" | Does NOT route to Avi (word boundary) |
| "How do I navigate" | Routes to Avi (question, "navigate" doesn't trigger) |

