## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| Too many questions routed to Avi | Can add rate limiting later if needed |
| False positive question detection | Conservative patterns, question mark is primary signal |
| Breaking existing behavior | Word boundary fix prevents "aviation" false positives |
